"The Firedoglake Writers’ Foundation is starting a new project called Occupy Exchange: a fellowship program that will send skilled Occupiers on visits to other Occupy encampments, where they will share their knowledge on the subjects their hosts need help with the most. Afterwards, our fellows will write up their experiences and lessons-learned and share them with the rest of the world."
